snippet.title: Stickers for You - Official Indie Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
This game was created for game streamers. It is nothing but pain. We do not recommend purchasing this game except for distributors. All you have to do is collect 100 stickers hidden in a closed city. But you probably won't be able to complete it alone.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3006450/Stickers_for_You/
